Added .aliases and cleaned up some plugins

Started using an `.aliases` file to store the aliases, with the proper
sourcing of the file added to .zshrc as well.

On the plugin side, I finally fixed the autocomplete problem with nvim
command line.
I've also added a linter/formatter for git commits.
